        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Challenges and Ethical Considerations"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Despite their potential, LLMs also pose significant challenges:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "orderedList",
        "attrs": {
          "tight": true,
          "start": 1,
          "type": null
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Bias"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": LLMs can inadvertently learn and perpetuate biases present in their training data, leading to skewed or unfair outcomes."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Misinformation"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Their ability to generate realistic text raises concerns about the spread of misinformation and deepfakes."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Resource Intensity"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": Training LLMs requires substantial computational power and energy, raising sustainability concerns."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "bold"
                      }
                    ],
                    "text": "Interpretability"
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": ": The complexity of LLMs makes them difficult to interpret, posing challenges in understanding their decision-making processes."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
